  <!-- EN: HESCO wall -->
  <USAC_HESCO.label>艾斯科墙</USAC_HESCO.label>
  <!-- EN: A bunker wall made of a collapsible wire mesh container and a heavy-duty fabric lining. It is typically used as a temporary or semi-permanent dike or blast wall. -->
  <USAC_HESCO.description>一种由可折叠的金属丝网容器和重型织物内衬制成的掩体墙。通常被用作临时或半永久性的堤坝或防爆墙。</USAC_HESCO.description>
  
